subject to a subsequent check or inspection.</li><li>The quality organisation is to have a <strong>database of delivered declarations of conformity.</strong> This database must be available for consultation by the parties involved as well as the administration. The data security of this database must be guaranteed and its management must be in compliance with privacy laws. A policy with associated procedures must also be in place to ensure the confidentiality of sensitive information.</li><li>The quality organisation must be <strong>impartial</strong> and is not allowed to have any members or directors who also carry out airtightness measurements themselves.</li></ul>"},"naam":{"nl":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Voorwaarden","en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","en":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"en":"<p>The quality organisation submits an application for accreditation to the Energy and Climate Agency of Flanders (VEKA). This application is to provide at least the following information:</p><ul><li>the details of the applicant</li><li>a description showing that the conditions are duly met.</li></ul><p>VEKA provides this application form for this purpose.</p><p>After examining the application, VEKA will make a decision on the application.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"<p>De kwaliteitsorganisatie dient een aanvraag voor erkenning in bij het VEKA. Deze aanvraag bevat minstens de volgende gegevens:</p><ul><li>de gegevens van de aanvrager</li><li>een beschrijving waaruit blijkt dat aan de voorwaarden voldaan is.</li></ul><p>Het VEKA stelt daarvoor dit aanvraagformulier ter beschikking.</p><p>Na onderzoek van de aanvraag zal het VEKA een uitspraak doen over de aanvraag.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>De kwaliteitsorganisatie dient een aanvraag voor erkenning in bij het VEKA. 